    public class ViewMoodActivity
extends android.support.v7.app.AppCompatActivity
implements MPView<MoodPlus>
    This is for viewing mood events. It will show all attributes of a mood from a participant, except their user name. If a location is attached to a modd then a navigation marker will appear to view on a map.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Carlo, Carrol
